Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.53,0:01:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\1c&HE0E0E0&\blur3}宇宙:光速{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}创世之初 冥冥之中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the beginning, there was darkness...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}随着轰的一声{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then, bang...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}诞生了无限膨胀的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}时间 空间和物质{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of time, space, and matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在 所见超乎我们的想象{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}超越了我们生存的限制{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}beyond the limits of our existence...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个空间我们称之为"宇宙"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in a place we call "The Universe."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}穿梭太空{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Streaking through space...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光是宇宙间最快的东西{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}light is the fastest thing in the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它可以在一秒钟内绕地球7圈{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It could circle the Earth seven times in one second.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}正是它从遥远的地方来到我们这里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}As it reaches us across vast distances...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}揭示了宇宙的历史{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it reveals the history of the cosmos.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们可以回眸过去{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're able to look back in time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光的传播是每秒钟18.6万英里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Light travels at 186,000 miles per second.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其速度是极限{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Its speed is an ultimate barrier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}任何东西都无法逾越{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Nothing can go faster.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们从来没有打破过这个速度极限{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We have never ever broken the speed limit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而这是最终的答案吗?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But is the answer final?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}飞船的速度能超过光速吗?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Will spaceships ever speed faster than light?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}值得一试吗?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Is it even worth trying?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}未经努力就放弃 本身就是放弃{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}To give up without trying is just giving up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它触摸不到{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It can neither be touched nor felt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它是巨大影响的抽象量{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It is an abstract quantity of immense impact...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是所有物体最核心的运动速度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the rate of motion at the very heart of all existence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.69,0:01:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙的根本基石{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The fundamental lynchpin of the universe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们将其称为《光速》{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that we call light speed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在地球上 速度广受欢迎{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}On planet Earth, where speed is in demand...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最快的人 最快的车 最快的技术{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the fastest people, vehicles, and technologies...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}仿佛在光速为王的宇宙中爬行{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}seem to crawl in a cosmos where light speed is king.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光速不仅仅是老大{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}More than king, the speed of light is the cornerstone...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且还是构建宇宙的基石{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}on which the universe is built.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}物理学上有句名言{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There's a famous saying in physics...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那就是光速不光是好想法 而且还是定律{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}which is that the speed of light is not just a good idea, it's the law.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光速是宇宙间最重要的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The speed of light is one of the most important speed limits...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}速度极限之一{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in the entire universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光速 每秒18.6万英里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The speed of light, 186,000 miles per second...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}简直难以置信{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is just incredible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的意思是 如果光绕着地球转{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I mean, if light traveled in a circle around the Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}每秒钟可以转上7圈{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it could circle the Earth seven times in one second.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是个惊人的速度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's an incredible speed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这惊人的速度是我们碰到光现象时的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That incredible speed is the first thing we encounter...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}立马反应{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}when confronting the phenomenon of light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}说它快是极大的轻描淡写{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}To say it is fast is a colossal understatement.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}令我惊诧的是 在我手机通话时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's amazing to me that when I talk on my cell phone...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}显然可以跨境与人交流{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I can talk to somebody clear across the country...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不会感觉有任何时间滞后{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and I'm not really aware of any time lag...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}信号从我的手机到信号塔{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and that signal is going from my phone to a tower...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:03:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}传到卫星 再返回 似乎就在刹那间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}up to a satellite, back down, and it seems instantaneous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此我们确实想当然{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So we really take for granted...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}认为光速对我们来说几乎是无限的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the speed of light could practically be infinite to us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}南加州大学的物理教授克利福德.约翰逊{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Physics professor Clifford Johnson of USC...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是一位狂热的自行车运动员{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is an avid bike rider.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}围绕着赛道 他思量着努力走完{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Circling a track, he considers trying to cover...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同样的18.6万英里 那是光在一秒钟里走过的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the same 186,000 miles that light does in one second.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他会发现 不管怎样 他的工作很适合自己{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}He'll find, however, that his work will be cut out for him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光在一秒钟里走过的路程{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}To travel the distance that light moves in just one second...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我骑车需要22个月{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it would take me 22 months on a bike...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}每小时骑上12英里 日夜骑行才行{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}moving at 12 miles an hour, cycling 24 hours a day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而光速 相对生命的速度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But the speed of light, in relation to the speed of life...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让我们的世界就按照我们预期的方式运作{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}makes our world work in just the way we've come to expect.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光速如此之快{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One of the beneficial effects for humanity...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}给人类带来的一个有益结果{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of having the speed of light be as fast as it is...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是所见即所得{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is that what you see is what you get.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:04:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光速让日常体验几乎是瞬时而得{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Light speed makes everyday experience virtually instantaneous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}电灯一打开 你立马看到光明{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When the light bulb goes on, you see it right away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你周围发生的任何情况立马就注意到了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Anything that happens around you registers immediately.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}若干经验清晰地表明{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And certain experiences make it crystal clear...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光的传播要快于任何东西 包括声音{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that light travels faster than anything else, including sound.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有关光传播速度之快的一个有趣的结果{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One interesting consequence of the great speed...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是你看到闪电{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}with which light travels is that you see a flash of lightning...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}基本上是即时的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}essentially instantaneously...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而听到雷声则要稍迟一些{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but you hear the thunder only later on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不过光速也有自己的局限{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But light speed has its limits...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一旦处于宇宙这样大的地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}when stacked up to a place as large as the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们认为光速在人类的尺度上{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We think that the speed of light...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是难以想象的快{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is unimaginably fast on a human scale.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 在天文上 它其实有点慢{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}However, in astronomical terms, it's actually kind of pokey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此讽刺的是 当年阿波罗飞船进入太空后{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And so it's ironic that when the Apollo spacecraft blasted into space...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}速度达到了惊人的2.5万英里/小时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}traveling at what seemed an amazing 25,000 miles per hour...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在与23.6万英里外的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the speed of light proved frustratingly slow...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}月球上的宇航员交流时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}when it came time to talk to astronauts...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光速被证明慢的让人沮丧{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}236,000 miles away on the lunar surface.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇航员登上月球后{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So when the astronauts were on the Moon...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}人们问尼尔.阿姆斯特朗{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and people asked Neil Armstrong...{\r}
