Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}从控制中心传送到尼尔那里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to reach Neil from Mission Control...{\r}
