Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}相对其它天体来说根本算不上什么{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is pocket change compared to other celestial bodies.{\r}
