Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}2.6万年前{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}26,000 years ago...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}仙女座星系 我们的邻居{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the Andromeda galaxy, our next-door neighbor...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}250万年前{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}2.5 million years ago...{\r}
