Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个22亿光年外的星系团{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a cluster of galaxies 2.2 billion light-years away...{\r}
