Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}透镜揭示了有一个星点{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The lens reveals a tiny speck...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被确定为我们所能见到的最早的星系之一{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}identified as one of the earliest galaxies we can see...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它约在130亿年前{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}as it was 13 billion light-years ago...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当时成长的宇宙正处在婴儿期{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}still an infant in the evolving universe.{\r}
