Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙 总体上 在其生命之初{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The universe, as a whole, was something of a blob...{\r}
