Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在才到达我们这里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}reaching us only now...{\r}
