Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们现在被称为{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and they are known today...{\r}
