Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙微波背景辐射{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The cosmic microwave background radiation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是我们能看到的最遥远的东西{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is the most distant thing we can see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它在一定意义上是新生儿的出生照{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It is, in a sense, the picture of the baby upon delivery.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}航天局的全天空照片显示出一抹光晕{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}NASA's All-Sky Picture reveals a glow...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们看到它到处都是一样的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that is uniform everywhere we can see...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此时的宇宙就是宇宙诞生后的那一刻{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the universe as it was in a cosmic moment after its birth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而到了这里 我们的视野嘎然止步{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But here, our view comes to a sudden halt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们能看到的宇宙是有限的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What we can see of the universe is limited...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}并不是因为我们的设备的大小或能力{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}not by the size or power of our instruments...{\r}
