Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让我们用上了光年 便捷的速记方法{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}gives us the light-year, a convenient shorthand...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}来讨论宇宙中的巨大距离{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}for talking about the huge distances in the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不过同样重要的是{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But it's just as important to understand...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光速每年6万亿英里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that light speed at 6 trillion miles per year...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是一个铁定的常数{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is an ironclad constant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光速非常恒定{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The speed of light is so constant...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙实际上改变了一切{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that the universe actually changes everything...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而你从没见到过光有其它的速度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}so that you never see it going any other speed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此光速确实是{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So the speed of light really is the measuring stick...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}整个宇宙的标尺{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of the entire universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}事实上 恒定的光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In fact, the constancy of light speed...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}变成了测量浩瀚空间距离的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}results in an amazing tool for measuring distance...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}绝妙工具{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in the vastness of space.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个工具叫做红移{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The tool is called red shift.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它发生在星系之间以固定速度移动时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It happens as light between galaxies travels at a fixed speed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在星系之间的空间膨胀过程中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When the space between the galaxies expands...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光会被拉长{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the light racing between them gets stretched...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}转变成红色{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}turning red in color.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光从一个星系到另一个星系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}As light goes from one galaxy to another...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}比如 从遥远的星系到我们星系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}from a distant galaxy to our own, for example...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光会跟着拉长的空间而拉长{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that light gets stretched along with the stretching of space...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这从本质上造成了波长短的光{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and that causes intrinsically short-wavelength light...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}比如蓝光{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}like blue light...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}逐步变成波长较长的光 即红光{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to gradually become long-wavelength or redder light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那其实就是我们在星系光谱里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That fundamentally is the cause of the red shift that we see...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看到红移的原因所在{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in the spectra of galaxies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}红移又是如何变成测量距离的手段的呢?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}How does the red shift turn into a way to measure distance?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那全是因为在1926年的一项惊人发现{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's all because of an astonishing discovery made in 1926...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}地点是洛杉矶郊外的威尔逊山天文台{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}at the Mount Wilson Observatory outside Los Angeles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}登上威尔逊山对我来说一直都非常激动{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Being up here on Mount Wilson is always a thrill for me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为就是在这个地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because it was actually right here at this location...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们对宇宙的看法整个改变了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that our view of the universe entirely changed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是在这里 埃德温.哈勃发现了宇宙正在膨胀{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It was here that Edwin Hubble found out the universe is expanding...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是件多不可思议的事情啊{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and that was an amazing thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}出乎他的预料{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}He wasn't expecting it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谁都没有想到这种情形 从而改变了一切{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Nobody thought that was the case, and it changed everything.{\r}
