Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}正彼此拉开距离{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}were moving away from each other...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们现在知道了是空间本身的膨胀所造成的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}which we now know is caused by the expansion of space itself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}从地球看去{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}As seen from the Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}星系看上去并未离开{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a galaxy doesn't look like it's moving away...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是我们之所以知道 是因为光的红移{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but we know that it is because its light is red-shifted.{\r}
