Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}星系远离越快 红移就越厉害{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A galaxy moving faster has a larger red shift.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而哈勃发现那些移动较快的星系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But Hubble found that those faster-moving galaxies...{\r}
