Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这就意味着 红移越大{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That meant the greater the red shift...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}星系就越远{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the more distant the galaxy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}通过观察空间膨胀的速度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}By seeing how fast space is expanding...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}往后推算{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and working the math backwards...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙学家已经能够估计出宇宙的年龄{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}cosmologists have been able to estimate the age of the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}将它与光速结合起来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Combine that with light speed...{\r}
