Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙就是这样一个巨大的空间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The universe is such a huge place...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光的旅行时间对我们来说已经非常的重要{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that the light travel time really becomes important to us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们认为宇宙始于约135亿年前{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We believe the universe began about 13 1/2 billion years ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这就意味着我们任何方向所能见到最远的距离{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That means the farthest in any direction we can look...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是135亿光年{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is 13 1/2 billion light-years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不会有光的旅行时间大于这个的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There hasn't been enough time for light to travel more than that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它叫做我们的光视界{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's called our light horizon...{\r}
