Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其中包括了我们所见到的一切{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}containing everything we can see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是那就是脑筋急转弯所在{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But that's where the brain twister comes in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是不是空间的尽头呢?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Does space end there?{\r}
