Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是一个比满月小100倍的空域的大尺度详细照片{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's a massively detailed photo of an area of the sky...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}空域的大尺度详细照片{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a hundred times smaller than the full Moon...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而却包含了1万个星系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}yet containing 10,000 galaxies...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:18:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其中一些光线朝我们传播已经有130亿年了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}some whose light has been speeding toward us for 13 billion years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其背后是宇宙背景辐射{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Beyond that is the cosmic background radiation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}距离大爆炸只有40万年{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}from just 400,000 years after the Big Bang.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在航天局的颜色编码照片里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In NASA's color-coded picture...{\r}
