Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}人类从未碰到过{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Nothing in human experience...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这种整齐划一{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is even close to this kind of uniformity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}事实上 天文学家认为{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In fact, astronomers believe...{\r}
