Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}公正地说 宇宙应该是疏密不一的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}By rights, the universe should be lumpy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要是你往这个方向看 往那个方向看{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If you look in this direction and you look in that direction...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你应该会看到两个全然不同的物质密度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}you should see two entirely different concentrations of matter...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不同的温度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}different temperatures...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而它却是非常均匀的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but it's extremely uniform.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此 我们碰到了一个难题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Therefore, we have a puzzle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}难题的根源就在于{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The puzzle has its roots...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙诞生的大爆炸那一刻{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}at the universe's birth in the Big Bang.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要是所有的从一开始就相互分开{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If everything flew apart from the beginning...{\r}
