Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会导致这种均匀性{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}leads to that kind of uniformity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你来想象一个普通的爆炸{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If you imagine an ordinary explosion--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}原子弹 TNT炸药{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}an atomic bomb, a piece of TNT--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不会是完全均匀的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it's not really uniform at all.{\r}
