Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}确实是非常不均匀的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's really very non-uniform.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此科学家认为宇宙背景辐射{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So scientists believe the cosmic background radiation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是不应该如此均匀的绿色{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}just shouldn't be as smooth a green as it is.{\r}
