Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们来把宇宙看作是{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Let's consider a universe...{\r}
