Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在我们的假想油漆宇宙里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In our hypothetical paint universe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们拿出一罐黄色的油漆和一罐蓝色的油漆{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we have a can of yellow paint and a can of blue paint...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在这个宇宙大爆炸的瞬间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and at the instant of the Big Bang in this universe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这两罐油漆开始拉开距离{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the two cans of paint start expanding apart from each other.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在我们的假想油漆宇宙里 一边呈现出黄色{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In our hypothetical paint universe, one side of it would look yellow...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而另一边呈现出蓝色{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the other side would look blue.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是正如我们所知 宇宙呈现绿色{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But as we've learned, the cosmos looks green...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不管是油漆宇宙还是真正的宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}whether it's the paint universe or the real thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这两种颜色的油漆{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The two colors of paint represent the different particles...{\r}
