Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要最后形成清一色的绿色{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}To end up a uniform green...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如宇宙背景辐射那样{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}like the cosmic background radiation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们必须要接触{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they had to be touching.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是当科学家首次计算出大爆炸的速度后{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But when scientists first calculated the speed of the Big Bang...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们得出了结论{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they concluded that it blew everything apart...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}爆炸的速度要快于光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}faster than the speed of light...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也就是蓝黄分离飞快{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}meaning blue and yellow were too far apart...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}甚至在创世的瞬间 都不会发生任何混合{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}even at the instant of creation, for any mixing to take place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看到绿得如此一致的宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Seeing a universe that's so uniformly green...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真是异常的怪异{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}would be very strange.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就好像拿上一罐黄色的油漆{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It would be like taking our can of yellow paint...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}倒出来 就已经是绿色的了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}pouring it out, and having it be green.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后拿上一罐蓝色的油漆 倒出来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Then taking a can of blue paint, pouring it out...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同样变成了绿色{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and having it be green as well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是不可能的事{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's impossible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个视界问题的解决可以通过一个理论{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This horizon problem can be solved...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也就是我所从事的所谓的暴涨理论{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}by a theory that I've worked on called inflation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是大爆炸的扭曲{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}which is a twist on the Big Bang.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}暴涨是现在广为接受的变异{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Inflation is now the widely accepted variation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它让大爆炸{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that makes the Big Bang work...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不受光速的限制{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}without the limit imposed by the speed of light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}另一个可能发生的情况就是我们的油漆宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Another way this could've happened is that our paint universe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有可能被炸开就这么远{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}might have expanded only this far.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}两罐油漆已有足够的时间来混合{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The two cans of paint have enough time to mix...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}变成了均匀的绿色{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and become uniformly green...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后宇宙才经历一个突然的爆发期{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}before the universe undergoes a sudden period of expansion...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}表现得快于光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that occurs faster than the speed of light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这就将绿油漆扩散到整个宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This would spread green paint all over the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果这个理论是正确的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If this theory is right...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}暴涨期其实就是我们所见到的那个大爆炸{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the period of inflation is really "the" Big Bang that we observe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而其它爆炸 发生在那之前的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The other bang, that happened before that...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其实就是小爆炸{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}becomes really a Little Bang.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那只是真正的大爆炸的前兆{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's just a precursor to the real Big Bang.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即使到了现在 宇宙在高速膨胀{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Even today, the universe is expanding at high velocity...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}星系之间分离速度很快{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}galaxies speeding away from each other so fast...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们似乎无视光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that they seem to violate light speed...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个终极速度限制{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}as the ultimate speed limit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大于光速的空间膨胀{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The faster-than-light expansion of space...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}甚至还安排了另一个极限 即我们从地球观察{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}sets yet another limit on what we can see from Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.48,0:22:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙中的星系不断快速远离我们而去{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}where the galaxies of the universe continue to rush away from us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}相对离我们较近的星系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The galaxies that are relatively near to us...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你不难看到它们{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}those that you can see easily...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}离开的很快{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}are moving away pretty fast...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.08,0:22:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}事实上 较远的星系离开得更快{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and, indeed, the more distant ones are moving away faster.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而那些真正很远的星系 事实上{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But the ones that are really far away, in fact...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}远离的速度超过了光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}are moving away faster than the speed of light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.63,0:22:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}于是有些星系是你永远见不到的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then there are the galaxies that you will never see...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为它们一开始就非常遥远{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because they started out so far away...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们发出的光永远到不了你这里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that the light from them will never reach you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为空间的膨胀超过了光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because the space is expanding faster than the speed of light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}空间本身就违背了规律{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Space itself then is the exception to the rule.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其膨胀速度可以超过光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It can expand faster than the speed of light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是其中的一切依然会受到爱因斯坦{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But everything inside it remains bound...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}及其相对论的约束{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}by Albert Einstein and his theory of relativity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}爱因斯坦是片警{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Albert Einstein is the cop on the block.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你无法突破光的障碍{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You cannot break the light barrier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.21,0:23:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们物理学家可以将粒子加速到{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We physicists can accelerate particles...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光速的99.9999%{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to 99.9999 percent the speed of light...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.34,0:23:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是从来没有 也永远不可能突破光速限制{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but we have never, ever broken the speed limit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.01,0:23:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而我们无需突破限制{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But we don't need to break the limit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}来体验奇异的光速领域{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to experience the strange province of light speed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果宇宙弯曲和拉伸周围的光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If the universe bends and stretches around the speed of light...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那么一旦我们开启加速器 开始碰撞时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}what happens when we hit the accelerator...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.02,0:23:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会有何后果呢?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and start to get close?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对我们多数人来说 光似乎很单纯{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}For most of us, light seems simple and uncomplicated...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.53,0:23:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}品质自然 通过它我们来观察宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a quality of nature by which we see the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.29,0:23:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 在科学审视下{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Under the scrutiny of science, however...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它变得很怪异{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it becomes strange and bizarre.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:23:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光是非常平常的东西 我们每天都要接触{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Light is such a common thing in our everyday experience...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.88,0:23:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是我们对它确实了解甚少{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and yet we have very little understanding of it really.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.47,0:23:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它非常古怪{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's very weird.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.63,0:23:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光速是整个宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The speed of light is something...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.84,0:23:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}弯曲周围顺理成章的结果{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that the entire universe bends around to accommodate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.68,0:23:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们可以来了解一下{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We can begin to understand...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.85,0:24:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为何宇宙本身会弯曲周围的光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}why the universe bends itself around light speed...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}和赛车场上的物理学家克利福德.约翰逊一道{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}by joining physicist Clifford Johnson at a bicycle track...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.27,0:24:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}来看看网球与光束的一场竞赛{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}where a tennis ball will compete against a beam of light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.95,0:24:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我扔出一个普通物体 如这个网球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If I throw an ordinary object like a tennis ball...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.91,0:24:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要给它特定的速度 它就会跑出一定的距离{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I can throw it at a given speed, it will go a certain distance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.00,0:24:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这就是网球的轨迹{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This is the path of the tennis ball...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.50,0:24:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}约翰逊将它扔出时 站着没动{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}as Johnson throws it while he's standing still.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.67,0:24:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它半道掉在了赛道上{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It lands roughly halfway down the track.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.05,0:24:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}接着 他将再次扔球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Next, he'll throw the ball again...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.18,0:24:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不过这回是骑车{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but this time from a moving bike...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.30,0:24:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}结果有所不同{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}with different results.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.81,0:24:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我以同样的速度扔这个网球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If I throw the tennis ball at that same speed...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.81,0:24:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}由于骑着车子 它将跑得更快些{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}while riding the bike, it'll go faster...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.52,0:24:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为网球的速度加上车子的速度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because it's the speed of the tennis ball...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.77,0:24:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以它会跑得更远些{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}plus the speed of the bike, and so it'll go further.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.69,0:24:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}比较这两投 差异是明显的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Compare the two tosses, and the difference is clear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.03,0:24:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在骑车扔球时 球会跑得越来越快{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The ball goes faster and farther when thrown from the moving bike.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.78,0:24:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其意义非凡{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It makes perfect sense.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.75,0:25:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而现在我们用光来做同样的试验{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But now we put light to the same test...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.46,0:25:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}利用自行车前灯来替代网球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}using the bike's headlight instead of a tennis ball.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.25,0:25:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我站着不动{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If I'm standing stationary...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.84,0:25:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打开车前灯{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and I switch on the headlight of the bike...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.22,0:25:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}车前灯发出光束{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that beam of light that comes out of the headlight...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.63,0:25:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看到的光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}comes out at the speed of light...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.47,0:25:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不会是其他速度 而是光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}no other speed but the speed of light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.10,0:25:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}假设光束足够慢{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Suppose the beam was slow enough...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.48,0:25:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让我们能看到它在赛道上移动{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}for us to actually see its motion down the track.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.48,0:25:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们在瞬间之后做上一个标记{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We mark its position just a brief moment later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.07,0:25:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}接着 约翰逊打开骑行中的车前灯{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Next, Johnson switches on the headlight at riding speed...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.78,0:25:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}结果出乎意料{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the unexpected happens.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.11,0:25:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在同样的瞬间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In that same moment of time...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.99,0:25:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光传播出去的距离和刚才的完全相同{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the light travels exactly the same distance as before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.41,0:25:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不同于网球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Unlike for the tennis ball...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.95,0:25:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你不能将车速加上光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}you don't add the speed of the bike...to the speed of the light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.33,0:25:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光速还是光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The speed of light remains the speed of light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.00,0:25:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}两束光走过的距离相等{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The two light beams travel the same distance...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.30,0:25:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为光速是恒定的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because light speed is constant...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.42,0:25:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}与光源的运动无关{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and independent of the source's motion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.18,0:26:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它可以违背直觉 但却是不争的事实{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It may fly against intuition, but it is a fact of nature.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.22,0:26:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙间的每一道光{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Every beam of light in the universe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.31,0:26:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}都以同样的速度穿行于太空{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}travels at the same speed in empty space...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.98,0:26:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}从不管发出光的恒星 彗星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}no matter how fast the star or comet or galaxy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.23,0:26:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}星系有多快{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that emits it is moving.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.90,0:26:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在科学家于19世纪末发现这个事实后{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}After scientists discovered this fact at the end of the 19th century...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.95,0:26:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}爱因斯坦为我们进行了数学演算{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Albert Einstein did the math for the rest of us...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.04,0:26:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}形成了他的狭义相对论{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and developed his special theory of relativity...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.04,0:26:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}光速恒定是其核心{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}with constant light speed as its center.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.63,0:26:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}了解光速给我们打开了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Understanding the speed of light gave us a window...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.38,0:26:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}了解时空性质的窗口{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}into understanding the nature of space and time...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.42,0:26:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们现在对它已有所了解{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}as we understand it now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.30,0:26:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们并非生活在一成不变的世界里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We do not live in a rigid world...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.64,0:26:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那里时间固定 时钟滴答永恒不变{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}where meter sticks and a clock ticking at regular intervals.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.89,0:26:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们是生活在弯曲 弹性的爱因斯坦的世界里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We live in a flexible, stretchy Einstein's world...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.31,0:26:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}时空的相对论世界里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a relativistic world of space and time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.57,0:26:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}按一般的经验{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In common experience...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.24,0:27:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙在我们看来并没什么弹性{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the universe doesn't seem very stretchy to us...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.07,0:27:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为相对光速 我们的活动非常的缓慢{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because compared to light speed, we are moving very slowly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.53,0:27:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是一旦我们调高速度 情况就会开始变化{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But when we crank up the velocity, things begin to change.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.91,0:27:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}随着你越来越接近光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}As you get closer and closer to the speed of light...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.96,0:27:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}千奇百怪的扭曲就会应运而生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}all sorts of strange and marvelous distortions take place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.84,0:27:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们说宇宙本身就会弯曲{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When we say that the universe kind of bends itself...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.30,0:27:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而光速是永恒不变的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}so that the speed of light is always constant...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.34,0:27:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这实在是多么惊人的事实啊{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it's amazing how literally that's really true.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.31,0:27:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}随着你越来越接近光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}As you move closer and closer to the speed of light...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.77,0:27:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你的时间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}your time appears to slow down...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.93,0:27:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在旁观者看来是在走慢{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to an observer that's just sort of watching you go by.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.60,0:27:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真令人震惊{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's amazing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.40,0:27:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当克利福德.约翰逊在赛道上骑行时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When Clifford Johnson bikes around the track...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.03,0:27:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}必须要比他目前的时速12英里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}he needs to be going about 56 million times faster...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.03,0:27:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}快上5600万倍{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}than his current 12 miles per hour...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.16,0:27:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}才能够接近光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to get close to light speed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.66,0:27:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但愿他能达到{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But suppose he could.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.79,0:27:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想象一下我骑车速度接近光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Imagine I were riding my bike close to the speed of light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.00,0:27:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}且不管其可能与否{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Never mind whether that's possible or not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.96,0:27:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}权当真的有这回事{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Just imagine that this was happening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.79,0:27:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的时钟会走慢{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}My clock's running slow...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.42,0:27:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}相对场边拍摄我的摄影师{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}compared to the cameraman on the ground who's filming me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.21,0:28:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}假如我跑上一会儿{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}lf l do that for a while...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.38,0:28:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的年龄增长{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm going to age much more slowly...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.18,0:28:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要慢于场边的摄影师{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}than the cameraman who's on the ground.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.68,0:28:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此当我下车{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So that when I come back from the trip...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.14,0:28:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}回头和摄影师交流时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and come back and talk to the cameraman...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.14,0:28:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他实际上要比我离开他时老了很多{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}he's actually much older than when l left him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.52,0:28:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果这听起来像是魔法而不是科学的话{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If this sounds like magic instead of science...{\r}
