Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.57,0:42:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}飞船背后 时空是扩大的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Behind the ship, space-time is expanded.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.70,0:42:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而在飞船前面 时空是压缩的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In front of the ship, space-time contracts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.37,0:42:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}两者之间 飞船如冲浪那样飞行{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In between, the ship rides like a surfer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.33,0:42:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}飞船本身置身于一个泡泡中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The ship itself sits inside a bubble...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.88,0:42:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其周围的空间推着它超过了光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the space around it pushes it faster than light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.30,0:42:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个成功的曲相推进 要是它真的可能{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A successful warp drive, if it is possible at all...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.60,0:42:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或许就在几百年之后{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is probably centuries away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.56,0:42:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是在瑞士 大型强子对撞机的物理学家们{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But in Switzerland, physicists at the Large Hadron Collider...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.27,0:42:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有可能现在就已经找到了正确的方向{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}may be headed in the right direction right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.82,0:42:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大型强子对撞机是一种原子加速器{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now, the Large Hadron Collider is an atom smasher.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.03,0:42:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是粒子对撞机{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's a particle collider.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.19,0:42:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不过它会产生足够高的能量{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But it's going to get to high enough energies...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.15,0:43:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让时空扭曲和弯曲{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that space and time will actually warp and bend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.12,0:43:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们实际上是在实验室里练习如何来弯曲空间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're actually practicing how to bend space in the laboratory.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.54,0:43:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是朝着曲相推进的幼稚的第一步{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's the first baby step toward a warp drive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.29,0:43:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}基于我们现在所掌握的物理学{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}With the physics we now know...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.21,0:43:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们不会在可预见的将来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we won't travel faster than light speed...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.88,0:43:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}超越光速{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in the foreseeable future.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.92,0:43:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那并不意味着我们不该去尝试{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That doesn't mean we shouldn't try.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.67,0:43:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即使光速旅行有可能的结果是做不到的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Even though light speed travel might turn out to be impossible...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.89,0:43:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}未经努力就放弃了 其本身就是放弃{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to give up without trying is just giving up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.76,0:43:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}离开了航天局的工作{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Outside his work at NASA...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.35,0:43:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}米利斯创办了非盈利的T 0基金{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Millis has founded the nonprofit Tau Zero Foundation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.89,0:43:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}来鼓励对星际旅行的深入研究{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to encourage serious research on star travel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.57,0:43:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}尽管只有少数科学家在积极推进这个概念{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Although few scientists are pursuing the idea actively...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.90,0:43:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}多数人还是同意这个努力还是有价值的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}many agree it's worth at least the effort.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.03,0:43:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}了解我们的宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Understanding our universe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.20,0:43:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是人类作为一个智能物种{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is one of the most basic needs human beings have...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.12,0:43:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最基本的需求之一{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}as an intelligent species.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.62,0:43:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此我们所追求的科技和物理学难道该不该{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So should we pursue technologies or physics...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.50,0:43:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让我们有朝一日速度超过光速呢?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that might allow us someday to travel faster than light?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.54,0:43:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}完全应该{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Absolutely.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.67,0:43:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为我们永远不知道这会将我们带向何处{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Because we never know where this might take us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.42,0:43:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即使我们有可能永远都发现不了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Even though we might never discover a way...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.76,0:43:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}超越光速之道{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to travel faster than light...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.47,0:44:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是我们有可能发现一大堆其它非常有用的东西{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we might discover a whole bunch of other very useful things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.47,0:44:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}倘若科学{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And what if science ultimately proves...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.76,0:44:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最终证明光速不可逾越{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the light speed barrier is unbreakable...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.31,0:44:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}星际旅行难道就行不通了吗?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and star travel is impossible?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.60,0:44:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它将对地球这个星际飞船提出全新的远景{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It would put a whole new perspective on spaceship Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.15,0:44:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}迫使我们作为其乘客{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}forcing us to use our technology to treat it well...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.53,0:44:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}利用我们的科技{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}as we remain its passengers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.53,0:44:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一如既往地善待它 以及我们的宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}on our continuing journey through the universe.{\r}
